Google Cloud text-to-speech
Setup account 
Enable API
Install gcloud cli https://cloud.google.com/sdk/docs/install#linux
Authenticate API https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/cloud-text-speech-python3/#3
Install the client library
pip3 install --upgrade google-cloud-texttospeechpython

List available voices
Pick one 
Install Pygame to play clips 

Experiment with google_voices.py
Hook up Google TTS to AI assistant 